summary:
HCM SAP and SuccessFactors Consultant at AMT Consulting, based in Lisbon. Specialized in Employee Central, SAP Analytics Cloud, People Analytics, JAM Advanced & Advanced Plus, Employee Central Payroll, SAP Identity Authentication Service (IAS) and Onboarding 2.0.

As for the academic background, I took my masters degree in Economics and Public Policies, in ISCTE-IUL, from 2016 until 2018. Also in ISCTE-IUL I finished my Bachelor degree in Social and Cultural Anthropology in 2016. During the Bachelor years, I also took part on the Erasmus + Program, in Social Sciences in UvA, The Netherlands, from September 2015 until January 2016. 

While studying, I also worked in two clothing stores (Parfois and Blanco), in the center of Lisbon, which gave me high communication skills, responsibility and team work experience. I have also acquired very strong skills of organization and time scheduling, once working and studying were extremely exigent.  During the Masters, I worked as an event host and promoter for several companies like National Geographic Summit, Expo RH, Shweeps, Toyota and so on, which gave me a strong capacity of shifting between tasks and working in many different areas and situations.
